---
import Icon from "astro-icon";

---

<ol class="items-center sm:flex">
    <li class="relative mb-6 sm:mb-0">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div
          class="z-10 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-red-100 rounded-full ring-0 ring-white dark:bg-red-900 sm:ring-8 dark:ring-gray-900 shrink-0"
        >
          <Icon
                aria-hidden="true"
                pack="mdi"
                name="creation"
                class="w-5 h-5 text-red-800 dark:text-red-300"
            />
        </div>
        <div
          class="hidden sm:flex w-full bg-gray-200 h-0.5 dark:bg-gray-700"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-3 sm:pr-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Creación
        </h3>
        <time
          class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
          >1995</time
        >
        <p
          class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
        >
        Nuestra historia comenzó a raíz de la 
        identificación de una necesidad
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="relative mb-6 sm:mb-0">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div
          class="z-10 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-red-100 rounded-full ring-0 ring-white dark:bg-red-900 sm:ring-8 dark:ring-gray-900 shrink-0"
        >
          <Icon
                aria-hidden="true"
                pack="ic"
                name="baseline-foundation"
                class="w-5 h-5 text-red-800 dark:text-red-300"
            />
        </div>
        <div
          class="hidden sm:flex w-full bg-gray-200 h-0.5 dark:bg-gray-700"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-3 sm:pr-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Evolución
        </h3>
        <time
          class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
          >2007</time
        >
        <p
          class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
        >
        Nuestra dedicación nos ha permitido destacar y 
        convertirnos en líderes indiscutibles en nuestro sector.
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="relative mb-6 sm:mb-0">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div
          class="z-10 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-red-100 rounded-full ring-0 ring-white dark:bg-red-900 sm:ring-8 dark:ring-gray-900 shrink-0"
        >
          <Icon
                aria-hidden="true"
                pack="mdi"
                name="podium-first"
                class="w-5 h-5 text-red-800 dark:text-red-300"
            />
        </div>
        <div
          class="hidden sm:flex w-full bg-gray-200 h-0.5 dark:bg-gray-700"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-3 sm:pr-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Actualidad
        </h3>
        <time
          class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
          >2023</time
        >
        <p
          class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
        >
        Seguimos avanzando, innovando y superando las expectativas de nuestros clientes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>